SUEZ CANAL.
DNC 10.
NGA HAS UPDATED LIBRARY H1048040 OUT OF CYCLE TO SUPPORT
THE RECENT CHANGES TO THE SUEZ CANAL. THIS LIBRARY
IS AVAILABLE ON THE UPDATED LIBRARIES SECTION OF
THE DNC WEBSITE AND MUST BE UPLOADED BEFORE THE
NEXT VDU PATCH, WHICH WILL BE AVAILABLE ON
21 AUG. THE LIBRARY CAN BE DOWNLOADED
FROM THE NGA NIPR WEBSITE AT
https:www.geointel.nga.mil/products/dnc/#updated
OR FROM THE SIPR SITE. FOR URGENT SERVICE,
CONTACT NGA NAVSAFETY, DSN: 547 5455,
PHONE: 800 362 6289 OR 571 557 5455,
E-MAIL: NAVSAFETY@NGA.MIL OR MSG TO
NGA NAVSAFETY WASHINGTON DC OR
E-MAIL: MCDDNC@NGA.MIL.
